div.p: Dendrogram obtained from the agglomerative hierarchical cluster analysis of 188 Salvia officinalis leaf essential oil compositions. (C1) α-thujone/camphor chemotype, (C2) α-humulene/α-thujone chemotype, (C3) β-thujone/α-thujone/camphor chemotype, (C4) 1,8-cineole/camphor chemotype, and (C5) sclareol/α-thujone chemotype.
